
LOCAL STORAGE-
Local Storage is the place where all your data gets saved.

GET METHOD-
to get the value of local storage -
localStorage.getItem('name of the variable whose value u wanna have');

SET METHOD-
to set the value of local storage -
localStorage.setItem('name of the variable',the value u want to set);
Also u can set the value inside that method only ,even if u have declared the variable globally if u are getting the value of a variable in certain method. 

Auth guard ts file is the place from where redirection must happen.

One must create a auth service file in order to match the desired conditions.

